<p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;晴空澄澈，微风轻拂，带着初夏的温柔与活力。为丰富校园体育文化生活，提升同学们的身体素质，培育团队协作意识，让同学们在运动中“羽动健康，轻享生活”。2025年6月5日下午，经管学子们齐聚羽毛球馆，一场羽毛球预赛在此激情上演。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>赛事开启</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1749566378620.png" alt="1749566378620.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1749566378620.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1749566393897.png" alt="1749566393897.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1749566393897.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;挥拍锋芒显，奋勇争先机男单赛场，选手们动作矫健，网前扑杀迅速，后场扣杀有力，羽毛球划出道道弧线。多拍相持考验着选手的耐力与技巧，汗水挥洒间目光依然专注。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>青春力量 与你相约</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1749566429580.png" alt="1749566429580.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1749566429580.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1749566441041.png" alt="1749566441041.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1749566441041.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1749566463727.png" alt="1749566463727.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1749566463727.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;巾帼英姿展，羽球竞荣光女单赛场，女选手技术细腻，网前小球处理得当，进攻时也能果断发力，落点精准。比赛不乏逆转好戏，落后选手沉着调整实现翻盘；也有选手凭借稳定发挥和强大心理一路领先。选手们灵动身影与穿梭的羽球，共同展现了赛场活力。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>羽动健康 &nbsp;轻享生活</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"><strong>圆满落幕</strong></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1749566348710.png" alt="1749566348710.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1749566348710.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p><span style="font-size: 19px; font-family: 宋体;"> &nbsp; &nbsp;这场羽毛球的对决，不仅是技巧与耐力的博弈，更是热血与热爱的共鸣。师生们在挥拍拼搏中感受热血力量，在汗水淋漓中领悟坚持的意义。相信带着这份运动场上的激情与斗志，经管学子将在学习与生活的“赛场”上继续勇敢拼搏。未来，我院也将持续丰富此类活动，让学子们在丰富多彩的校园生活中，不断书写属于自己的成长诗篇。</span></p>